OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWilloughby 'hurt' over     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSchofield's lies on affair 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Holly Willoughby has said it was "very 
OL,6, hurtful" to discover her former co-host
OL,7, Phillip Schofield lied to her about his
OL,8, affair with a younger colleague.       
OL,10,FOn Friday, Schofield confirmed he had  
OL,11,Fhad a relationship with a younger male 
OL,12,FITV employee while still married.      
OL,14,FIn a statement, Willoughby said: "When 
OL,15,Freports of this relationship first     
OL,16,Fsurfaced, I asked Phil directly if this
OL,17,Fwas true and was told it was not.      
OL,19,F"It's been very hurtful to now find out
OL,20,Fthat this was a lie."                  
